    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好拥有世界上最好的洗衣店了吗？将一个小型洗衣店转变成洗衣帝国！在《Laundry Store Simulator》中发现以下特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/35ce1f242695f41bb87f5c2dbcaaf8ec.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span>将一个小型洗衣店打造成一个繁荣的商业帝国！升级您的设备，设计并扩展您的商店，雇佣员工等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dffd9f1dd15bcf81ad04fc47e032c751.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span>升级您的设备以提供卓越的清洗服务！投资高质量的洗衣机、烘干机、熨烫设备，甚至是自动洗衣机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/bdcfb43f1816e84d5a81e3867e9f1b8d.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span>创造一个时尚且吸引人的空间来吸引顾客！提供舒适的座椅、温馨的装饰，以及更多有趣的元素来欢迎您的顾客！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/aeb422b48a175c6ed5396c4211f9fdb6.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span>通过解锁新区域和功能来发展您的洗衣业务，提供免费服务以吸引更多顾客！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/acb5eca87034e4324de0333678a5a4e5.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span>组建一个敬业的团队来高效管理您的洗衣店！雇佣合格且经验丰富的洗衣店员工，如洗衣工、烘干工等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/18ca5080fe0acb1567953981689ff52a.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span>通过销售清洁用品来增加您的利润，成为一站式洗衣需求商店！提供各种清洁产品，包括洗涤剂、织物柔顺剂、去污剂等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/4c735fb3070490a5b85200a69599b4a4.avif?t=1770372539\" width=600 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放你的创造力，为独特的顾客设计定制衬衫！画任何你喜欢的图案，打印出来，看看他们自豪地穿上你的作品吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/d4b0deafe366f4535b4dc8037bc7531e.poster.avif?t=1770372539\" width=640 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/d4b0deafe366f4535b4dc8037bc7531e.webm?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150440/extras/d4b0deafe366f4535b4dc8037bc7531e.mp4?t=1770372539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
